Ask HN: How have you started recently using AI in your personal or work life?
text: Over the past months, while reading interesting stories on automated text and image generation, I've been feeling a small amount of FOMO about not yet taking advantage of any of it. I'm a Project Manager on software projects (mostly front and backend related) and feel that I could be improving my life or my team's but I'm wasting this opportunity. Any ideas that the community feels are worth looking into? Merry Christmas to all that celebrate it!

Help Locked out of 10 years Gmail account
text:
Due to the recent LastPass debacle, I decided to cycle my Gmail passwords. Boy that was a mistake!!

Gmail has decided that I can't log in with "just" my password. The new password is correct. It then asks me for my old password, which I put in correctly. Then it tells me I can't log in anyway. :(

Occasionally it will give me a QR code to scan. But I can't scan it on my phone, since my phone is logged out.

I can't log in to my recovery account, because (like a fool) I changed the passwords simultaneously. Now both are locked.

Somebody help! My account name is edgeofepsilon@gmail.com (the recovery email should match my HN username). I'm locked out of a decade+ of correspondence, recovery, and historical data.
